bio:
Syndus is a Bosmer weapons and armor merchant who runs a shop in The Ragged Flagon. He becomes available after completing the first available city influence quest given by Delvin Mallory for the Thieves Guild. His shop is in an alcove just south of the entrance from the Ratway.
Syndus is one of the earned merchants through completing City Influence quests, along with Herluin Lothaire, Arnskar Ember-Master and Vanryth Gatharian.
name: Syndus
